<p>We are able to host school or extracurricular groups at our department at McGill University. We have a variety of activities for all ages, offered in French or English. Typical visits vary in length, and may involve museum tours, lab tours, short demos, or hands-on activities. <a href="mailto:outreach@physics.mcgill.ca">Contact us</a> for information or to request a visit. Visit date and language are subject to volunteer availability.</p>
